                      /
                      <span>3</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-06-12</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book guides the traveler/reader to interesting places in New Mexico that are also historic. It is set up so that someone driving along a road can read about the various towns and sites along that road. It is a great book that I found very useful to read and use. <P>Ginger</span>
                  
              
